<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/head') %>
  <title>Academy — WirfonCloud</title>
</head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/navbar') %>

<section class="page-banner" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(1,153,239,0.7), rgba(0,95,163,0.85)), url('/images/IMG_20230625_133031_342.jpg');">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>WirfonCloud Academy</h1>
    <p>Your gateway to a cloud computing career.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="courses" class="section anchor-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Courses</h2>

    <h3 class="group-title">Fundamentals of IT</h3>
    <div class="cards-grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h4>Linux</h4>
        <p>Master the Linux command line, file system, permissions, and shell scripting — the foundation of cloud infrastructure.</p>
        <div class="card-actions">
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline btn-sm">Preview</a>
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Sign Up</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h4>Networking</h4>
        <p>Understand TCP/IP, subnetting, routing, DNS, and the network fundamentals every cloud engineer needs.</p>
        <div class="card-actions">
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline btn-sm">Preview</a>
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Sign Up</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h4>Python</h4>
        <p>Build automation scripts and cloud tooling with Python — from basics to working with cloud SDKs.</p>
        <div class="card-actions">
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline btn-sm">Preview</a>
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Sign Up</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h3 class="group-title">Intermediate to Advanced</h3>
    <div class="cards-grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h4>AWS Practitioner</h4>
        <p>Lay the groundwork for your AWS journey and prepare for the Cloud Practitioner certification.</p>
        <div class="card-actions">
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline btn-sm">Preview</a>
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Sign Up</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h4>AWS Solutions Architect</h4>
        <p>Design resilient, scalable, and cost-effective architectures on AWS — and earn the SAA certification.</p>
        <div class="card-actions">
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline btn-sm">Preview</a>
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Sign Up</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h4>Ansible</h4>
        <p>Automate configuration management and application deployment with Ansible playbooks and roles.</p>
        <div class="card-actions">
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline btn-sm">Preview</a>
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Sign Up</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h4>Terraform</h4>
        <p>Provision infrastructure as code across AWS and beyond using HashiCorp Terraform.</p>
        <div class="card-actions">
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline btn-sm">Preview</a>
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Sign Up</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="learning-paths" class="section section-alt anchor-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Learning Paths</h2>
    <div class="cards-grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h4>DevOps Engineer</h4>
        <p>A guided path from Linux and Git through CI/CD, Docker, Kubernetes, and infrastructure as code.</p>
        <a href="mailto:contact@wirfoncloud.com?subject=Interest%20in%20DevOps%20Engineer%20Path" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Register Your Interest</a>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h4>Cloud Engineer</h4>
        <p>Become a confident AWS cloud engineer — networking, compute, storage, security, and architecture.</p>
        <a href="mailto:contact@wirfoncloud.com?subject=Interest%20in%20Cloud%20Engineer%20Path" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Register Your Interest</a>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h4>Cyber Security</h4>
        <p>Learn cloud security fundamentals, identity and access, encryption, and threat detection.</p>
        <a href="mailto:contact@wirfoncloud.com?subject=Interest%20in%20Cyber%20Security%20Path" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Register Your Interest</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="more" class="section anchor-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">More</h2>
    <div class="text-center">
      <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg"><i class="fa-brands fa-discord"></i> Join WirfonCloud Community on Discord</a>
    </div>

    <h3 class="group-title">Testimonials</h3>
    <div class="testimonials-grid">
      <div class="video-card">
        <div class="video-wrap"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/aByknzTTOaY" title="AWS Deep Dive" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>
        <p class="caption">AWS Deep Dive on Amazon S3</p>
      </div>
      <div class="video-card">
        <div class="video-wrap"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/n4qHUXrRcds" title="re:Invent Recap" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>
        <p class="caption">AWS re:Invent Recap at WirfonCloud</p>
      </div>
      <div class="quote-card">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-quote-left"></i>
        <p>"WirfonCloud's training gave me the confidence and the skills to land my first cloud role. The hands-on labs make all the difference."</p>
        <div class="quote-author">
          <div class="avatar-placeholder"></div>
          <span>Alumni Name</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="quote-card">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-quote-left"></i>
        <p>"The mentorship and community at WirfonCloud accelerated my career change into cloud engineering by months."</p>
        <div class="quote-author">
          <div class="avatar-placeholder"></div>
          <span>Alumni Name</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
